---
title: Honey Mustard Chicken & Chive Mash with Sauteed Leek & Carrot
description: Pair classic ingredients and easy cooking techniques with a few flavourful tweaks - like chives in mashed potatoes and wholegrain mustard plus honey on tender chicken - and your weeknight dinner just got a whole lot more exciting!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bf4a00d30006c4e5b729d12-acae37e5.jpg
